text:
@WHO Does the new coronavirus affect older people, or are younger people also susceptible?

@WHO: People of all ages can be infected by the new #coronavirus (2019-nCoV). WHO advises people of all ages to take steps to protect themselves from the virus. https://t.co/WbZyDtr0qi
